==English==

===Etymology===
From [[dis-]] + [[interest]]

===Pronunciation===
*{{audio|en-us-disinterest.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
'''disinterest'''
#{{uncountable}} A lack of interest; [[indifference]]; [[apathy]].
#{{uncountable}} The [[absence]] of selfish [[bias]] or [[self-interest]]; [[impartiality]] or [[detachment]].

===Verb===
{{en-verb}}
#{{transitive}} To cause to lose interest; to [[bore]].

